ZooKeeper - hadoop distributed coordination service.
It's give us a set of tools to build distributed application that can safely handle partial failures.
It helps to keep all task in synchronize mode and make a reliable application. Zookeeper coordinates all nodes in a cluster.
ZooKeeper::
  Maintaining configuration info - Sharing config info to all nodes
  Naming - Find a machine in a cluster of 1000 server
  Providing group service - Leader election and more
  Providing distributed synchronization
